Description: Gerimo - Virtual Tablet & Input Controller
 Requires the Gerimo Android app (free on Google Play Store) to function.
 .
 Turn your Android into a professional and customizable input controller for PC.
 Everything you touch, draw, or type on your device is transmitted as genuine
 mouse, keyboard, or pen input with extremely low latency and high precision.
 .
 Perfect for:
  - Artists and designers using Android as a drawing tablet with stylus input
  - Students and professionals who need a remote desktop controller
  - Power users creating AI shortcuts, macros, and automations
  - Supports multiple monitors with precise input mapping
 .
 Connections: WiFi, Bluetooth, and USB with consistently low latency.
 .
 Features:
  - Pen Module: High precision graphics tablet for drawing and note taking apps
  - AI Shortcut Assistant: Create shortcuts and macros with AI from your device
  - Gesture Control: Navigate with touch gestures, pinch to zoom, trackpad mode
  - Keyboard Input: Type on Android, every keystroke sent in real time to PC
  - Window Control: Minimize, maximize, or close apps with a single tap
  - Undo/Redo: Instant access to Ctrl+Z and Ctrl+Y
  - Home screen widgets for instant shortcut actions
 .
 Languages: English, Arabic, German, Spanish, French, Italian, Korean,
 Portuguese, Russian, Turkish, Chinese, Hindi, Japanese, Indonesian and more.

